  "subject": "Update path to SDNC rest interface in policy-management-service",
  "commit_message": "Update path to SDNC rest interface in policy-management-service\n\nThe path to SDNC has been updated from  \"/restconf/operations\" to  \"/rests/operations\".\nHence, the update is needed in policy-management-service (PMS).\nThe path is made configurable so that the PMS can also work with older versions of SDNC.\n\nThe ODL password has also been updated in the latest version of SDNC.\n\nChange-Id: If43c8632b4012437f9502fdac17ffa23f3a6719f\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-3193\nSigned-off-by: RehanRaza <muhammad.rehan.raza@est.tech>\n",
